  "url": "https://www.tamilmirror.lk/\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd/\u0b95\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0ba3\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd-\u0baa\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd-\u0b87\u0ba9\u0bbf-\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1-\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd/175-300140",
  "time_ut": 1657460269,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0ba3\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba9\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Glass cases are now ventilated",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the current crisis and precarious economic situation in the country, the production of bakery products, including pan, will end in two to three days, All Sri Lanka Bakery Owners Association President N.K. Jayawardena has warned.",
        "He informed that this situation will occur due to the prevailing fuel crisis, shortage of raw materials and increase in prices, and he mentioned that production has stopped in 50 percent of the bakeries and the rest of the bakeries will stop working very soon.",
        "He pointed out that as the responsible member, he had mentioned earlier that the bakery industry was facing a huge threat and would further decline due to the ongoing fuel crisis.",
        "However, he said that even when he informed the Minister of Power and Energy about this fuel crisis, he has not yet received any response from the Minister.",
        "He mentioned that bakery production also comes under the category of essential services, but added that no steps have been taken so far to revive the bakery industry."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
      "body_line_ents_list": [
        [
          {
            "text": "two to three days",
            "label": "DATE"
          },
          {
            "text": "All Sri Lanka Bakery Owners Association",
